sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant UI as TUI Layer
    participant App as App Core
    participant Coord as Agent Coordinator
    participant LLM as LLM Provider
    participant Tool as Tool System
    participant DB as SQLite

    U->>UI: Type prompt + Enter
    UI->>App: Submit prompt
    App->>DB: Save user message
    App->>Coord: Create/run agent call

    loop Agent Loop
        Coord->>LLM: Send messages (streaming)
        LLM-->>Coord: Text delta / Tool call

        alt Text Response
            Coord-->>UI: Stream text to chat
            UI-->>U: Display response
        else Tool Call
            Coord->>Tool: Execute tool
            Tool-->>Coord: Tool result
            Coord-->>UI: Show tool execution
            Note over Coord,LLM: Feed result back to LLM
        end

        alt Context Window Full
            Coord->>Coord: Auto-summarize
            Note over Coord: Replace history with summary
        end
    end

    Coord-->>App: Agent turn complete
    App->>DB: Save assistant message
    App-->>UI: Update chat view
